{"id":1226,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":187,"title":"Conversation 97","subtitle":"Office Shredder Troubles","level":"B2","parts":15,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-97.1226/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-97-2023-10-01-16-07-10/0-conversation-97.mp3","transcript":"The paper shredder is jammed, again!\nAre you serious?\nThe repairman was just here last week and said it was fixed!\nI am going to try to fix it myself,\nbut I don't have a lot of experience with handiwork.\nYou're kidding.\nThey are such complicated machines,\nyou might end up making it worse.\nThat is a good point.\nWe need to face reality, that this machine is broken.\nIt is time to get a new one.\nThat sounds expensive.\nI don't know if the procurement department will approve the expense.\nLet's make an appeal to management and outline how many problems this causes.\nThat might persuade them.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:01:14","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"The paper shredder is jammed, again!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-97-2023-10-01-16-07-10/1.mp3","time_start":0.65,"time_end":3.33},{"position":2,"content":"Are you serious?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-97-2023-10-01-16-07-10/2.mp3","time_start":4.01,"time_end":5.63},{"position":3,"content":"The repairman was just here last week and said it was fixed!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-97-2023-10-01-16-07-10/3.mp3","time_start":5.63,"time_end":9.97},{"position":4,"content":"I am going to try to fix it myself,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-97-2023-10-01-16-07-10/4.mp3","time_start":10.24,"time_end":13.15},{"position":5,"content":"but I don't have a lot of experience with handiwork.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-97-2